727324f-b.text:
Main Street, west side, south fron 59th Avenue (foreground), showing the area where new housing developments will be erected. The dwellings under construction in the center background are on Horace Harding Boulevard, Main Street being on the extreme left
and is a new thoroughfare here.
P. L. Sperr  Anril 19, 1936
